data.description: This charming Cape Cod features 4 bedrooms. Two bedrooms on the first floor and two bedrooms on the second floor. There is a spacious family room off the kitchen. Great for big family gatherings. Newer Roof, Windows. Great backyard for entertaining. Also, an oversized garage. This property is close to shopping center and the Merritt parkway. Subject to short sale approval, working with bank now. 24-hour notice please.
